value.0: Many of these elves were called from Evermeet itself, highly trained in the art of archery. With their exceptionally keen senses, they serve as the scouts of Winya Ravana.

Dogma of Shevarash:  The greatest enemy of the Seldarine is Lolth, who sought the corruption of Arvandor and the overthrow of the Creator of the Elves. The greatest enemy of the Fair Folk is the drow, the debased followers of the Spider Queen who long ago were enmeshed in her dark web. Redemption and revenge may be achieved through the utter destruction of the drow and the dark deities they serve. Only then may the joy of life begin anew. Hunt Fearlessly!
